{
  "name": "Tornado Lord",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "modules/pf1spheres/assets/icons/spheres/weather.webp",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Weather sphere (Wind Lord (advanced)), caster level 10th.</p>\n<p>When you use control weather to affect wind, you may alter the path of a single tornado within range more precisely. Each round as a free action you may plot a course for the tornado, which may be up to 250 feet long and may have one turn of up to 90 degrees, plus one turn per 5 caster levels above 10th. Alternatively, you may cause the tornado to remain in one place. You can alter the path of a tornado caused by magically-altered wind combined with Climate.</p>\n",
